- [*if relevant*] s/he agreed to engage in another sexual act on that occasion with the accused or with any other person, or that s/he agreed to engage in another sexual act with the accused or another person on an earlier occasion."}, {"candidate_index": 4, "id": "7.3.6-c6-s1", "title": "7.3.6 Consent", "score": 0.08625560126031231, "chapter_key": "7", "section_key": "7.3", "text": "## Consent"}, {"candidate_index": 5, "id": "7.3.15.3-c5-s6", "title": "7.3.15.3 Care, supervision or authority", "score": 0.08544813426433152, "chapter_key": "7", "section_key": "7.3", "text": "1. the person submits because of force or the fear of force to that person or someone else;

